# 🚀 JavaScript Backend Development Journey

This repository contains my learning journey of Backend Development using  
Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, and modern backend development practices.

The goal of this journey is to learn how real-world backend systems work, how APIs are created, how databases are managed, and how professional scalable applications are built.

---

# 📚 What I Am Learning

- Backend Development Fundamentals
- Node.js Runtime
- Express.js Framework
- REST API Development
- MongoDB Database
- Mongoose ODM
- Authentication & Authorization
- JWT (JSON Web Tokens)
- File Upload Handling using Multer
- Error Handling & Custom API Responses
- Backend Architecture & Folder Structure
- Professional Project Setup
- Connecting Frontend with Backend
- Deployment & Production Setup
- HTTP Methods & Status Codes
- Postman API Testing
- Routing & Controllers
- Debugging Backend Applications
- Real-world Data Modelling

---

# 🛠 Tech Stack

